What is Genkai-Hyeonhae Community?

The Genkai-Hyeonhae meeting/community/activity focuses on the following points:

1) We try to explore networking and application technologies about the
   Internet that can lead both research & development and commercial sector.

2) Based on these technologies, we try to promote the
   information/community exchanges between Japan and Korea

3) And we try to extend this collaboration over Northeast Asia to build
   a real information infrastructure for information exchange and better
   understanding in Asia.

